<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Live Dispatch Wayplan Board</title>
  <style>
    body{margin:0;font-family:Arial;background:#020b18;color:#eef8ff;padding:32px}
    .sub{color:#fbbf24;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:3px}
    h1{font-size:42px}
    .card{border:1px solid rgba(56,189,248,.35);background:#071527;border-radius:18px;padding:22px;margin:16px 0}
    button{border:0;border-radius:14px;background:#f97316;color:white;padding:14px 18px;font-weight:900;cursor:pointer}
    .ok{color:#86efac;font-weight:900}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="sub">BRITIUM EXPRESS</div>
  <h1>Live Dispatch Wayplan Board</h1>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="ok">REAL PAGE LOADED</div>
    <p>This is not the dashboard shell. Vercel static file routing is now fixed.</p>
    <p>Next step is reconnecting the RPC content inside this page.</p>
  </div>
  <button onclick="location.href='/?ts=' + Date.now() + '#/dashboard'">Back to Dashboard</button>
</body>
</html>
